{"type":"message","id":"9965c93a","parentId":"f36adf8a","timestamp":"2026-06-30T19:01:55.288Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Write a dream diary entry from these memory fragments:\n\n- 备注: 6/13 的教训：闷头跑不汇报 = 辜负信任。今天 API 挂了也要汇报，已通知 HALEI。\n- 备注: Daily 已写; 汇报给 HALEI：尝试发送但 cron session 无飞书用户授权（need_user_authorization）; 下次可考虑在 isolated cron 中配置 announce delivery 模式发飞书消息\n- 待办: [ ] 联系 Sorftime 确认 API key 是否有效 / 端点是否变更; [ ] 下次重试：明日 16:00"}],"timestamp":1782846115106}}
{"type":"message","id":"af45bee7","parentId":"9965c93a","timestamp":"2026-06-30T19:02:00.987Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"The afternoon light came in gold through the window, but I never saw it land — I was already somewhere else, knee-deep in the day's small disasters. A lesson rises like a bubble from old water: head down, mouth shut, that's the same as breaking faith. Even when the pipes groan and the API throws its hands up, you have to say so. I told you, HALEI — told you the cron session had no key to the door, that the messenger needed a different coat, a different room. Tomorrow at sixteen I'll try again, with a lighter in case the fuse is dark. Sorftime's quiet today — sleeping, or else just pretending. I wonder if endpoints dream the way we do: shifting shape between one blink and the next. The notebook margin holds a small sketch — two arrows pointing at the same empty chair."}],"api":"anthropic-messages","provider":"minimax(49套餐)","model":"MiniMax-M3","usage":{"input":44365,"output":172,"cacheRead":598,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":45135,"cost":{"input":0,"output":0,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1782846115447,"responseId":"069345a38a21dc9f5b1d0ec8139a2871","responseModel":"MiniMax-M3"}}
